<refnamediv id='name'>
<refname>gfdf</refname>
<refpurpose>display disk free space of Gfarm file system</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv id='synopsis'>
<cmdsynopsis>
  <command>gfdf</command>
    <arg choice='opt'>-a</arg>
    <arg choice='opt'>-D <replaceable>domainname</replaceable></arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1 id='description'><title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<para>
<command>gfdf</command> displays disk usage and free space of
Gfarm file system.
</para>
</refsect1>

<refsect1 id='options'><title>OPTIONS</title>
<variablelist>
<varlistentry>
<term><option>-a</option></term>
<listitem>
<para>Displays only summary information of the Gfarm file system.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term><option>-D</option> <parameter>domainname</parameter></term>
<listitem>
<para>
Specifies a domain name of filesystem nodes to list the status
of disk free space. 
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term><option>-?</option></term>
<listitem>
<para>Displays a list of command options.</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</refsect1>

